去進行游說 每人都脫離同溫層進行游說 咁樣做就會提升返其中一戰「區議會」既勝算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">而依刻我覺得未睇到大家既團結 </span></span><br />\n我眼中既團結除左大家係有共識不分化 不割席依句口號之外 我仲想有深層次少少既解說亦都係我同一位社工朋友既共同見解 <br />\n一個良好既溝通或者良好既表達意見方式 重點都係想對方接收到意見 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而屌既方式其實對方未必可以即時吸收到 </span></span><br />\n首先佢會有一層隔膜先 會覺得你屌佢而唔係關心佢 <br />\n其實我地有得選擇用較好既表達方式 <br />\n以一句為例子 食咁快哽死你啊 同 慢慢食無咁易哽親 其實理想情況下 正常人都會較易接受後者 但唔排除有人係唔屌唔識醒 咁再作方法啦 <br />\n經過中大 理大兩戰 其實所有手足都心情沈重 大壓力 負能量 無力感 和理非一樣係手足 我絕對明白大家 <br />\n因為我都身處依個狀況 除左場運動之外仲要失埋戀無左精神支柱 我同咩都無曬無咩分別 <br />\n但大家都唔可以將情緒宣洩喺手足身上 真係要宣洩就跟我方法去跑步出下汗練下氣 健身練下力 我唔想再見到互屌既情況 我地無分化既本錢 面對乜毛都好 直接無視或不推文<br />\n<br />\n我地要注重每個細節 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抱平等 尊重 互助 分享想法</span></span> 比意見手足作參考<span style=\"color: red;\">而非指指點點</span> <br />\n畢竟依場運動無大台 我講既 大家講既都只係意見 集思廣益 岩既有成效既就去做 大家不坊多講概念如何促進合作 和勇既目標都只會想提高運動成功嘅機會 <br />\n另外點解我一而再再而三多謝和理非不割 係因為我明白到即使有一千個最勇既勇武 <br />\n同時面對武力不對等 如果無和理非既民意去支持其實依一千人既心理壓力會好龐大 前線既資源都會變得更有限 撒退又會變得更難 和勇不分好嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝和理非</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔係一個階段性勝利既人 <br />\n我認為既勝利係落實五大訴求且共產黨倒台 <br />\n但我地都唔可以忽略左已有初步進度既事實 <br />\n中共既醜陋更為人所關注 中共更明顯地表露一國一制 港共既無能 暴力 其實好多黑材料我地應該善用 就文宣方面 <br />\n<br />\n我想比一個建議之前亦有人提及 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣不坊可以貼埋係自己屋企樓層電梯位</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得帶手套 </span></span>因為好多人其實唔敢係連儂場睇 <br />\n因為太多藍絲亂篤灰 好多人唔想被影相<br />\n<br />\n另外埋大既手足唔好再周圍講自己出返黎啦 <br />\n贏左之後你係煲底再講都未遲 有幾次有幾位被困手足出到黎即刻打電話大大聲報喜 我明你好激動 但我地唔知身邊既係咩人 煲底之後你地應承左請我食飯 希望你地煲底時仲記得我<br />\n<br />\n作為前線 我唔講自已夢境做過咩啦 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實每位手足係街 即使係黃店都唔應該講夢境</span> 老實講從八月到今日 我會有一種唔知自己得返幾多時間既感覺 被秋後算賬？ 被自殺？<br />\n我唔知依種係咩感覺 我只係一個普通人如果可以 我想快啲贏 追返女朋友 我唔想有咁耐空窗期 好驚佢比人追左 驚佢對我當初僅餘嘅愛都無埋 <br />\n但如果日後我再出唔到自己既感受post 大家應該會知咩事 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">可唔可以有手足代我走埋落去贏左依個極權？<br />\n可唔可以你日後既男朋友會全心全意令你日日都開心？</span><br />\n <br />\n完左區議會 <br />\n下一篇我會講戰術 新手勇武如何進化 勇武和理非戰場上如何有更好既配合<br />\n<br />\n希望大家推爆佢比多啲手足睇到 <br />\n或者俾多啲唔同意見或者提出問題 <br />\n我會盡量下一篇講埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"color: gold;\">贏左係起義 輸左係暴動</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人報仇</span><br />\n                                                   <span style=\"color: maroon;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">一位前線手足 <br />\n                                                       ？？？？？</div></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee1aefcfec986a5c76f8e1f6ef1e044447ab507","tid":1747512,"uid":207557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:05:13.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"7bc107d6d22e8674b6944745233eed640115d5ec","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"78e459e1e45dbbb50aa6df95862b9585f3bb25fb","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"4822ab5295a75f877dfa7ac0f1844fbd90728f21","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"5bdb5a6db1a99298fb0cc83495e7704a98d9ce2c","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"8a07da0deeafae20c9164bd8b6e9f36fffb29625","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"bea0e2c89109148c8b83dd94c050ad12ae0ad245","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"7e3a7370cca2c6b5155f51efcf59ccbdd5d06bc6","tid":1747512,"uid":207441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"1124"},{"pid":"6ffe1be4e3385090627aa84e002ea8723482fec3","tid":1747512,"uid":22969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76106d865c42fc7286c8ead6a79860adc1cbe710","tid":1747512,"uid":278149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a552f9165b3027eabc45a8bce4f0456ee7103e05","tid":1747512,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"香港人一定會好快贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你一定可以好快追番你女朋友<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e749ed2758666825dc86f3b6f3ccbf691ec33c8","tid":1747512,"uid":336561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"7點去排隊！！！！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d187f9499814b65c90e6f40f1890a8efc4d721","tid":1747512,"uid":175522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1649840c7d08d47ce736e0739ac29d7e6d391e38","tid":1747512,"uid":269773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"推， 多謝手足"},{"pid":"2d7e6a82ef866cd359f14628ed9f8ca1db07e1fa","tid":1747512,"uid":142319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb8a81b70da3d994e5bbfad0414b7f651c626d95","tid":1747512,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"push"}]}